title: Person of Interest - Simulation 336 742 [PART 2/2] (04x11)
author: POI - Best Of
comment: I will say when this first aired I legit screamed when Finch got shot and died. I actually thought for a second it was real.
You have no idea how relieved I was when "Simulation" word appeared
Can't believe that Harold died in this simulation, but it's a good thing that they reset to real time.
Greer is the best boss on TV. Loved this show since the premiere.
"I go to hell,  I am taking you with me" ---Reese 🙏🙏🙏
